OL,6,FJudge Rowlands criticised Gwynedd
OL,7,FCouncil for not investigating concerns
OL,8,Fabout Foden meeting girls alone as far
OL,9,Fback as 2019.
OL,11,FHe said: "It does appear to me that
OL,12,Fwhen real concerns were raised with
OL,13,Fthe council in 2019 they were
OL,14,Fdismissed.
OL,16,F"No note was even taken of anything
OL,17,Fthat was said. We now know he
OL,18,Fcontinued to offend. That's very
OL,19,Fconcerning indeed".
